{"tid":1192814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（極重要）行之前，想講下「非暴力」抗爭係咩","createTime":"2019-06-08T15:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T16:06:24.000Z","uid":40525,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"81c811a10b7b79d3d4607c2083b0af11672f6f04","tid":1192814,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:21:48.000Z","msg":"眾志啱啱出咗圖話會同大家非暴力抗爭， 希望大家唔好誤會。<br />\n<br />\n非暴力=/=鳩坐<br />\n非暴力=/=和平坐低<br />\n非暴力=/=唔推鐵馬<br />\n<br />\n喺坊間（民主派）嘅定義入面， 只要唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">意圖直接傷害人</span>， 都可以叫做非暴力抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n亦則係話， 好多人講嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">非暴力抗爭， 係包含使用合理武力嘅可能性（e.g 推撞）</span>， 只係目標唔係人。<br />\n<br />\n所以聽日大家執生， 睇住身邊嘅人。 最重要要睇住自己， 有香港人先到香港。<br />\n<br />\nP.S 雖然政治上的定義係咁， 但如果不幸去到法庭上， 都係會話你係暴力。 但如果目標唔係人都會有著數"},{"pid":"68aab8e3511731c872ae25eb8d32b0dc707a4c73","tid":1192814,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:22:49.000Z","msg":"-遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n-遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n-集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n-起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n-衝定唔衝，自己執生<br />\n-記得宗旨：不散<br />\n<br />\n溫和：<br />\n<strong>【長期置頂】69反送中遊行須知整合</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[懶人包] 第一次參加遊行的常見疑問Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【極重要】69遊行記得帶防Rfid卡套</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武： <br />\n<strong>食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[law撚］被捕人仕須知</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>［抗爭手冊］End game前準備</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ad44308e43d6a7c026cf60430140c2726590847","tid":1192814,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7879cae18b828da5684d3ba82c9fd27928c930","tid":1192814,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdcdfdf3788c276ca534e08ccd9e54822e776be","tid":1192814,"uid":143033,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ce841b9a333d7e85b7a136c63d2e26e4a29254e","tid":1192814,"uid":55493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:26:45.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒衝入去，佔金鐘應該算非暴力啦掛<img src=\"